      <scopecontent id="aspace_ee45317fee8fdd870b85bfdac268978c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of the papers of Henry I. Baldwin as secretary of the Yale School of Forestry's Class of 1922. The records document the activities of the class secretary, the school's 80th anniversary, and the Yale Alumni Association.</p>  
